# Frontend -> backend API base URL.
#
# LOCAL DEV: leave this UNSET. Requests fall back to the same-origin "/api"
# proxy in vite.config.ts, which forwards to the backend (no CORS needed).
#
# PRODUCTION / non-proxied: set this to the backend's base URL. The backend
# mounts its routes at the ROOT, so do NOT append /api or /api/v1 (that 404s):
#   VITE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
